thread.title: Astrid Beetson

author: Astrid Beetson
title: Astrid Beetson
text:
My family and I recently used Airport Rentals on the Sunshine Coast on our recent stay.
We booked a rental car via the website, the price we saw was what we paid. No surprise fees.
On our arrival at the Counter, just a few quick minutes to finalise paper work, and we were directed as to where our rental vehicle was.
Smooth transaction, hassle free , would recommend to anyone who needs a rental vehicle.
